{"tid":2161030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南蒙古：牧民抗議養豬場破壞他們的祖傳土地","createTime":"2020-08-17T10:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:50:27.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"206a23d4c47f66e1f4d139963a80ecd022fb7aa1","tid":2161030,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/southern-mongolia-herders-protest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fsouthern-mongolia-herders-protest%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21N5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=368522dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/southern-mongolia-herders-protest/</a><br />\n<br />\n8月13日，內蒙古自治區四子王旗烏蘭花鎮300多名示威者上街抗議中共持續破壞牧場消滅蒙古傳統文化。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙古（當地人更願意稱之為南蒙古）雖然不像西藏和新疆那樣知名，但也經常發生蒙古人抗議事件，他們稱中共正在摧毀他們的傳統文化與民族身分認同。<br />\n<br />\n中共早就將牧民定為抵制「中國化」的蒙古民族身分認同的代表。中共的策略就是以「生態」「現代化」或「減貧鬥爭」為由剝奪牧民的牧場，中共相信，這樣牧民就不得不尋找其他工作並放棄自己傳統的民族身分認同。<br />\n<br />\n去年8月26日，中共政府宣布新規定，允許畜禽養殖公司不必審批就可以佔用（蒙古牧民的）土地，當地政府也不可能反對其佔用土地。於是，在內蒙古烏蘭察布市四子王旗，七家漢族人開辦的養豬場佔用了當地蒙古族牧民的祖傳土地。<br />\n<br />\n隨後牧民發起抗議活動，儘管中共試圖阻止南蒙古像西藏和新疆那樣成為世界人權問題（的焦點），但這些抗議活動，特別是經外媒報道後，並非空無效果，70多天之前，這七家養豬場停止經營。<br />\n<br />\n然而，其中最大的一家養豬場又開始經營了。8月13日，四子王旗政府駐地烏蘭花鎮300多名牧民上街抗議，他們試圖進入當地政府大樓，但被警察阻止，並遭到毆打。南蒙古信息中心（Southern Mongolian Human Rights Information Center）發布抗議活動視頻，並再次呼籲國際社會支援牧民。"},{"pid":"22ebf01bffe18c561385d676742d87dc35fe3ea1","tid":2161030,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>Southern Mongolia: Herders Protest Pig Farming Destroying Their Ancestral Lands</strong><br />\n<br />\nOn August 13, more than 300 protesters took to the street in Wulanhua, while the CCP continues to destroy grazing land to eradicate Mongolian traditional culture.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>More:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://bitterwinter.org/southern-mongolia-herders-protest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwinter.org%2Fsouthern-mongolia-herders-protest%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21N5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=a119e89c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bitterwinter.org/southern-mongolia-herders-protest/</a>"},{"pid":"33ba330777d4d618c0bf8ee0f6d85963d649ba3f","tid":2161030,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"放養&gt;圈養<br />\n打獵&gt;種田<br />\n冒險&gt;人型豬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea95c04391288d6b01da0028940c82211451fe3c","tid":2161030,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33ba330777d4d618c0bf8ee0f6d85963d649ba3f","tid":2161030,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"放養&gt;圈養<br />\n打獵&gt;種田<br />\n冒險&gt;人型豬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"強逼蒙古人漢化，令蒙古人失去自己既民族認同（老祖宗既蓄牧業，文字語言都失傳，我還是世代相傳的蒙古人嗎？）"},{"pid":"a1b62083de8ee42324a7e582a3100ac7cf2e9def","tid":2161030,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb08da5eb31b852d5111137b0d6b8cac4aa9d78","tid":2161030,"uid":71210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"中共正仆街"},{"pid":"dc0daea2d4c92f2ebbd3bd02c818e6a21b96ed72","tid":2161030,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}